  "title": "BIM Archi/Structure Coordinator",
  "description": "<h2><u><strong>BIM Archi/Structure Coordinator</strong></u></h2>\n<p><strong>Visit https://ourengineers.com to apply or submit your CV for more job opportunities.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>· Coordinate with consultants, sub-contractors &amp; engineers.</p>\n<p>· Manage and prepare models and shop drawing to support the construction works</p>\n<p>· Coordination of structural works during construction process.</p>\n<p>· Good knowledge of structure and architectural details</p>\n<p>· Liaise closely with internal and external parties as well as the authorities to resolve structure design discrepancies and construction issues.</p>\n<p>· Assist in maintaining BIM systems and standards for construction projects</p>\n<p>· Liaise with Clients, Consultants and prepare/conduct weekly progress reports and technical meetings</p>\n<p>· Ensure the subcontractors and vendors follow the specifications and standards in the project VDC implementation.</p>\n<p>· Should have an experience in large scale projects</p>\n<p>· A good team player &amp; able to meet tight deadlines</p>\n<p>· Raise RFIs, oversee resolution of disputes/coordination issues with his/her respective trade subcontractors</p>\n<p>· Conduct clash-detection and conflict resolution.</p>\n<p>· Able to conduct QA/QC to the BIM models.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>· Degree in Civil Engineering or Architectural</p>\n<p>· Min 3 years of coordination experience</p>\n<p>· Familiar with Building &amp; Construction regulation of Singapore</p>\n<p>· Good knowledge of Structural Specifications &amp; Requirements</p>\n<p>· Experience on producing shop drawing- Structure / Architecture</p>\n<p>· Have experience with Substation/SP/LTA project is a MUST.</p>\n<p>· Must be expert and specialist in Revit and AutoCAD.</p>\n<p>· Should know (Revit, Navisworks &amp; BIM 360) as well.</p>\n<p>· Industry BIM Certification (Revit Professional, BCA BIM courses) is preferred</p>\n<p>· Fluency with Bluebeam or other markup and design review tools will be advantage.</p>\n<p>· Strong interpersonal skill and ability to develop positive relations with different stakeholders.</p>\n<p>· Self-driven and good time management</p>\n<p>· Knowledge of BIM is a MUST</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Visit https://ourengineers.com to apply or submit your CV for more job opportunities.</strong></p>",
